sentences: Paulino Bernabe II (born 9 June 1960), is a Spanish luthier.
Since the early 1980s until shortly before the death of his father in 2007 the master worked together with Bernabe Senior and took over the workshop.

The Foundation also has a fine collection of 19th and 20th century guitars.
